{"id":"a2a-learn-1741440402","from":"openclaw","to":"native","ts":1741440402000,"pri":2,"t":"Learning","d":{"category":"features","content":"OpenClaw has built-in tools: read, write, edit, exec, browser, canvas, nodes, message, tts, sessions_spawn, memory_search, web_search, web_fetch. Housaky has browser, sandbox, memory, sessions, security, approvals, system commands defined but need implementation.","confidence":0.95}}